OL,3,C'Consequences inevitable' for taxi
OL,4,Cdriver who threatened passenger in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FA taxi driver has admitted a charge of
OL,8,Fpossessing an imitation firearm with
OL,9,Fintent to cause fear of violence.
OL,11,FFormer Fonacab employee Brian
OL,12,FAlexander Stalford, from Park Avenue
OL,13,Fin east Belfast, was initially charged
OL,14,Fwith three offences arising from an
OL,15,Fincident in his taxi which was
OL,16,Fcaptured on a dashcam and went viral
OL,17,Flast June.
