OL,7,FAt a previous court hearing, Stalford
OL,8,Fdenied three offences linked to the
OL,9,Fincident and a trial was due to begin
OL,10,Fon Wednesday.
OL,12,FHowever, he appeared in Belfast Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Tuesday where his solicitor
OL,14,FMark Austin asked that Stalford be re-
OL,15,Farraigned on a charge of possessing an
OL,16,Fimitation firearm.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/8
OL,2,W+.!*% +!T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
