OL,4,Cdriver who threatened passenger in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FHe was then charged that on a date
OL,8,Fbetween March 1 and June 2, 2023 he
OL,9,Fpossessed a handgun resembling a
OL,10,F'Desert Eagle' self-loading pistol
OL,11,Fwith intent to cause fear of violence.
OL,13,FWhen the offence was put to him, he
OL,14,Fwas asked how he pleaded, and he
OL,15,Freplied "guilty."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/8
OL,2,W+.!*% +!T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
