OL,7,FFollowing this, Crown barrister
OL,8,FNatalie Pinkerton told Judge Donna
OL,9,FMcColgan KC that the prosecution was
OL,10,Fleaving two remaining counts 'on the
OL,11,Fbooks' and they were not being
OL,12,Fproceeded with.
OL,14,FThese counts were assaulting a front
OL,15,Fseat passenger and threatening to kill
OL,16,Fthe same male, on a date between March
OL,17,F1 and June 2, 2023.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/8
