OL,7,FJudge McColgan said that as Stalford
OL,8,Fhas admitted a "very serious charge",
OL,9,Fthe consequences were "inevitable" and
OL,10,Fhe was to be remanded into custody
OL,11,Fahead of sentencing.
OL,13,FMr Austin then addressed the Judge and
OL,14,Fasked that his client be granted
OL,15,Fcontinuing bail.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/8
