OL,7,FThis, he said, was to allow Stalford
OL,8,Fto be examined by a number of defence
OL,9,Fexperts including a psychologist which
OL,10,Fthe solicitor said "can often prove to
OL,11,Fbe extremely difficult" for defendants
OL,12,Fremanded in custody.
OL,14,FMr Austin added that Stalford "has
OL,15,Fbeen on bail for a somewhat
OL,16,Fsignificant period of time" and has
OL,17,Fabided by all conditions.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/8
