OL,7,FWhen asked what the Crown's view was
OL,8,Fregarding bail, Ms Pinkerton said "the
OL,9,Fprosecution would not be applying to
OL,10,Frevoke his bail" pending sentence -
OL,11,Fbut agreed that the consequences of
OL,12,Fhis plea were "inevitable."
OL,14,FJudge McColgan released Stalford on
OL,15,Fcontinuing bail and he was told to
OL,16,Freturn to court on Tuesday July 2nd,
OL,17,Fwhen he will be sentenced for the
OL,18,Ffirearms offence.
